## 4. MICRO-INTERACTIONS & ANIMATIONS

### 4.1 Animation Philosophy

> **Motion communicates meaning.** Heavy machinery moves with power and precision. Our animations mirror this: large movements are confident and swift; small movements are exact and controlled. Nothing wobbles, nothing bounces playfully. Easing curves favor `expo-out` for entrances and `power2.inOut` for transitions.

### 4.2 Global Animation Tokens

```css
:root {
  --ease-power-out: cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);      /* Primary entrance */
  --ease-power-in: cubic-bezier(0.7, 0, 0.84, 0);         /* Exits */
  --ease-smooth: cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);            /* General transitions */
  --ease-bounce-minimal: cubic-bezier(0.34, 1.56, 0.64, 1); /* Rare: button clicks */
  
  --duration-instant: 150ms;
  --duration-fast: 250ms;
  --duration-normal: 400ms;
  --duration-slow: 700ms;
  --duration-dramatic: 1200ms;
  
  --stagger-tight: 60ms;
  --stagger-normal: 120ms;
  --stagger-loose: 200ms;
}
```

### 4.3 Component-Specific Micro-interactions

#### A. Button Hover States
```
.btn-primary:
  idle: background #f9c500, shadow 0 0 0 rgba(249,197,0,0)
  hover: translateY(-2px), shadow 0 8px 24px rgba(249,197,0,0.35), background #e6b200
  active: translateY(0), scale(0.98), shadow 0 2px 8px rgba(249,197,0,0.2)
  transition: all 300ms var(--ease-power-out)

.btn-outline-dark:
  idle: border 2px solid #f9c500, background transparent
  hover: background #f9c500, color #0f0f0f, letter-spacing +0.02em
  transition: all 300ms var(--ease-power-out)
```

#### B. Card Lift & Shadow
```
.machine-card, .service-card:
  idle: translateY(0), shadow 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.06)
  hover: translateY(-6px), shadow 0 16px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.12), border-left-color #f9c500
  image: scale(1.05) with overflow:hidden container
  transition: all 400ms var(--ease-power-out)
```

#### C. Nav Link Underline
```
.nav-link:
  ::after pseudo-element:
    idle: width 0%, left 50%
    hover: width 100%, left 0% (transform-origin: center)
    transition: width 350ms var(--ease-power-out)
```

#### D. Scroll-Triggered Section Reveals (IntersectionObserver)
```
Strategy: Content below fold starts invisible, animates in when 20% visible.

.fade-up:
  from: opacity 0, translateY(40px)
  to:   opacity 1, translateY(0)
  duration: 700ms, easing: expo-out

.fade-left:
  from: opacity 0, translateX(-30px)
  to:   opacity 1, translateX(0)
  
.scale-in:
  from: opacity 0, scale(0.95)
  to:   opacity 1, scale(1)

.stagger-children:
  parent triggers, children animate with 80ms stagger
  each child: fade-up variant
```

#### E. Counter Animation (Stats Section)
```
Trigger: IntersectionObserver on stats section
Animation: Number counts from 0 to target over 2000ms
Easing: expo-out (fast start, gradual settle)
Format: Add "+" suffix, locale-aware separators
Example: 0 → 2,847 (over 2s)
```

#### F. Testimonial Marquee
```
Container: overflow hidden, white-space nowrap
Content: duplicated for seamless loop
Animation: translateX(0) → translateX(-50%) over 40s linear infinite
Pause: animation-play-state paused on hover
Edge masks: linear-gradient(to right, bg-color, transparent 5%, transparent 95%, bg-color)
```

#### G. Mobile Menu Entrance
```
Overlay: opacity 0 → 1, 300ms
Panel: translateX(100%) → translateX(0), 400ms, expo-out
Links: translateX(20px) + opacity 0 → translateX(0) + opacity 1, stagger 60ms
Close: reverse, power2.in
```

#### H. Image Reveal (Hero/Gallery)
```
Technique: Clip-path or scale reveal
.from-scale:
  container: overflow hidden
  image: scale(1.2) → scale(1.0) over 1.2s, power2.out
  simultaneously: opacity 0 → 1 over 800ms
```

#### I. SVG Line Draw (Process Timeline, Coverage Map)
```
Technique: stroke-dasharray + stroke-dashoffset
.line-draw:
  from: stroke-dashoffset = pathLength
  to:   stroke-dashoffset = 0
  duration: 1500ms per segment
  easing: power2.inOut
  trigger: scroll-into-view
```

#### J. Emergency Float Pulse
```
.emergency-float:
  animation: pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite
  @keyframes pulse:
    0%, 100% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(204,41,54,0.4); }
    50%      { box-shadow: 0 0 0 12px rgba(204,41,54,0); }
```

### 4.4 Parallax & Scroll Effects

| Element | Effect | Range |
|---------|--------|-------|
| Hero background image | translateY at 0.3x scroll speed | 0 to 100px over first viewport |
| Page hero backgrounds | translateY at 0.2x scroll speed | Subtle depth |
| Section dividers | Opacity fade 1→0.3 as next section scrolls over | CSS scroll-timeline if supported, fallback to JS |

### 4.5 Reduced Motion Support

```css
@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
  *, *::before, *::after {
    animation-duration: 0.01ms !important;
    animation-iteration-count: 1 !important;
    transition-duration: 0.01ms !important;
  }
  .testimonial-marquee { animation: none; }
  .counter { /* show final value immediately */ }
}
```

