## 8. CONVERSION FUNNELS

### 8.1 Conversion Philosophy

B2B conversions happen on **confidence**, not urgency. The funnels guide users from "I need a solution" to "I trust these people to provide it." Every CTA is a step toward a conversation, not an immediate transaction.

### 8.2 CTA Inventory & Placement

| CTA Text | Destination | Placement | Priority | Color |
|----------|-------------|-----------|----------|-------|
| **Поискайте оферта** | /kontakti (pre-filled) | Hero, Machine detail, Footer | P0 | Primary yellow |
| **Говорете с инженер** | tel:0878553273 | Header (desktop), Sticky bar (mobile), Emergency FAB | P0 | Emergency red |
| **Вижте машините** | /mashini | Home capability strip, About CTA, Footer | P1 | Outline dark |
| **Научете повече →** | Page/section | Cards, service items | P1 | Text link |
| **Сравни машини** | Modal | Machine cards (checkbox) | P2 | Outline |
| **Свалете каталог** | PDF | Downloads page, Machine detail | P2 | Primary |
| **Проверете наличност** | /rezervni-chasti | Spare parts hero | P1 | Primary |
| **Докладвайте авария** | Form modal | Emergency banner | P0 | Emergency red |

### 8.3 The Three Primary Funnels

#### FUNNEL 1: Machine Purchase
```
Awareness: Google Search → Landing on Home
  │
  ├─ Hero CTA: "Поискайте оферта" → /kontakti
  │
  └─ Or: Scroll → Machine Carousel → Click card → Machine Detail
           │
           ├─ "Request Quote" (form pre-filled with machine)
           │
           └─ "Compare with..." → Comparison tool → Decides → Request quote
```

**Conversion Rate Optimization (CRO) tactics:**
- Exit-intent modal on Machine Detail: "Still deciding? Our engineers can help. Call or leave a message."
- Machine detail page has NO sidebar distractions — single-column focus on specs + CTA
- Quote form asks: project type, timeline, budget range → qualifies the lead

#### FUNNEL 2: Service Request
```
Urgency: Breakdown occurs → Direct call OR visits /serviz
  │
  ├─ Mobile: Taps emergency number immediately (header CTA always visible)
  │
  └─ Desktop: Reviews services → Sees process timeline → Gains confidence
           │
           └─ CTA: "Докладвайте авария" → Modal form:
               • Machine model
               • Symptom description
               • Location
               • Urgency: [Normal / Same-day / Emergency]
               → Auto-email + SMS alert to Hydromotor team
```

**CRO tactics:**
- /serviz page loads with 24/7 number above fold on mobile
- Coverage map proves they service the user's region
- Certification wall proves competence

#### FUNNEL 3: Spare Parts Inquiry
```
Need: Parts purchaser needs component → /rezervni-chasti
  │
  ├─ Search by part number (if known)
  │
  └─ Browse by category → Select category → View typical parts
           │
           └─ Inquiry form:
               • Machine model (dropdown, auto-complete)
               • Part description or number
               • Quantity needed
               • Urgency
               → Response commitment: "Within 2 hours during business hours"
```

### 8.4 Form Strategy

**Smart Form Logic:**
```
Field: "Тип запитване" (Inquiry type)
  ├─ „Покупка на машина" → Show: Budget range, Project type, Timeline
  ├─ „Сервиз" → Show: Machine model, Symptom, Location
  ├─ „Резервни части" → Show: Part number, Machine model, Quantity
  └─ „Друго" → Show: General message field

Field: „Модел машина" → Autocomplete from machines.js
```

**Form Submission Flow:**
1. User submits
2. Inline validation on blur (no waiting for submit)
3. On submit: Button text changes to „Изпраща се..." + spinner
4. Success: Button becomes green checkmark + "Изпратено"
5. Confetti disabled. Instead: Subtle toast notification top-right
6. Analytics event fired: `generate_lead`

### 8.5 Post-Conversion Experience

| Funnel | Immediate Feedback | Next Step |
|--------|-------------------|-----------|
| Quote request | "Благодарим! Инженер ще се свърже с вас до 24 часа." | Show phone numbers prominently; "Want faster response? Call us." |
| Service request | "Заявката е приета. Очаквайте обаждане." | Display service ticket number; SMS confirmation if phone provided |
| Parts inquiry | "Проверяваме наличността. Ще отговорим до 2 часа." | Show typical response times; link to catalog downloads |
| Catalog download | "Каталогът е изтеглен" | Suggest related machines or services |

